Revision history for {{$dist->name}}

{{$NEXT}}

2.01	2016-02-18T09:45:04-0500

  [BUILD]

    * specify minimal required version of Path::Tiny

2.0	2016-02-16T17:23:01-0500

  * no changes since 1.6_01

1.6_01	2015-03-11T16:39:49-0400

  [API BREAKAGE]

    * Exceptions are now always thrown upon error.  The PrintError
      option and errmsg method have been removed

  [ENHANCEMENT]

    * configuration files may be searched for in one or more directories
      using the paths option

    * regularized the interpretation of ./ and ../ and relative paths
      in %include directives.  *should* be backwards compatible...

    * Logging via Log::Any for searching/reading/parsing configuration files

  [BUILD]

    * Switch to cpanfile
    * More author tests

1.6	2014-05-26T14:18:42-0400

 [ENHANCEMENT]

  * expanded (interpolated) variables may now be checked against
    wildcard variables (via the new ExpandWild attribute).


1.5	2013-08-30T16:00:49-0400

[ENHANCEMENTS]

   * new method, getbool, converts value to boolean


1.4	2011-08-23T12:03:22-0400

[ENHANCEMENTS]

  * attributes may be specified via the constructor

  * new attribute, 'dir' allows chdir'ing to specified directory
    before loading config files

[OTHERS]

  * switch to Module::Install
  * switch to GPL3


1.3	2006-09-21T09:19:36-0400

  * first release into the Wild
